Author: bulimicomrade
Text: She's so ignorant. People in other countries have EDs too. It's just that they're talked about a lot more in the US whereas they're a lot more taboo in many other countries.
i hate this "tHeY WaTcHeD AnTm AnD nOw TheY'RE AnOReXiC". No. Nobody starves themselves to a point where it is medically dangerous because someone on TV looked skinny.
